      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. I noticed some of the brands have a lot of fillers like corn or soy too. Is it better to stick to high protein even if it's more expensive, or should I be more worried about the actual fat content if he's still pretty active during walks?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
